  "description": "<i>Road Trip: Arcade Edition</i> is the GameCube edition in the <i>Road Trip</i> series of racing games. This game allows you to race tiny little toy cars around various oversized environments. Most of the cars resemble super-deformed versions of popular automobiles, but the actual model names are not used. There are dozens of tiny cars to collect.<br><br>Some of the tracks in this game appear to be scaled to the size of your racer, others take place in oversized real-world environments, like a house or a garden.<br><br>The usual racing game modes are present, single race, championship, and multi-player. Winning races allows you to purchase upgrades and other vehicles. You can also link this game with <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/road-trip-shifting-gears\">Road Trip: Shifting Gears</a>.",
